! Fising
[[ActiveRecall and SpacedRepetition System|https://docs.ankiweb.net/background.html]] in [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com/]], fishing with [[Anki algorithm|https://github.com/oflg/anki-algorithm]].

!! Install
Drag [[this plugin|$:/plugins/oflg/fishing]] to your TiddlyWiki.

!! Usage
# Add tag `Fish` to tiddler you would like to revise.
# Click {{$:/plugins/oflg/fishing/Buttons/fishing}} on the sidebar and select a revise group.

